### Test File Fix

The i18n test file has a `localStorage` mocking issue. The standard vitest fix:

```typescript
// Before each test:
beforeEach(() => {
  vi.spyOn(Storage.prototype, 'getItem').mockReturnValue(null)
  vi.spyOn(Storage.prototype, 'setItem').mockImplementation(() => {})
})
```

Or use `@vue/test-utils` config to stub `localStorage` globally.

### Shared `common.*` Keys

| Key | English | Used In |
|-----|---------|---------|
| `common.loading` | `"Loading..."` | Wiki, API Sources |
| `common.saving` | `"Saving..."` | Professions, Skills, API Sources |
| `common.save` | `"Save"` | Professions, Skills, API Sources |
| `common.cancel` | `"Cancel"` | Professions, Skills, API Sources |
| `common.edit` | `"Edit"` | Wiki, Agents (already exists) |
| `common.delete` | `"Delete"` | All views |
| `common.default` | `"Default"` | Agents (already exists) |
| `common.resetDefaults` | `"Reset Defaults"` | Agents, Professions, Skills |
| `common.upload` | `"Upload"` | Agents (already exists) |
| `common.generate` | `"Generate"` | Agents (already exists) |
| `common.generating` | `"Generating..."` | Agents (already exists) |
| `common.remove` | `"Remove"` | Agents (already exists) |

| Approach | Pros | Cons |
|---|---|---|
| Per-view namespace keys (chosen) | Organized, no key collisions, easy to audit | More keys to manage |
| Flat keys (`"loading"`, `"save"`) | Fewer keys | Collisions, unclear scope |
| Inline string extraction tool | Automated, no manual audit | Tooling overhead, may miss context |

- Positive: Mechanical change — no logic changes, only string replacement
- Positive: All 6 views follow the same pattern as existing i18n views
- Positive: `common.*` keys reduce duplication across views
- Negative: ~150 new translation keys to add to both en.json and zh.json
- Mitigation: Keys follow a predictable `viewName.elementName` pattern
